text.tspan: Disclaimer: This experiment will record your key presses or swipes and measure your reaction times.
It is anonymized and no other information is recorded.
This can be verified by looking at the code https://github.com/laurentperrinet/OEiL_OrientationPrecision

tspan.tspan: and on the publicly-available recorded data https://osf.io/3ytnp
